<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 09:15:42 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>路透调查显示，10月份中国工厂活动可能连续第六个月萎缩</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-factory-activity-likely-contracted-oct-sixth-month-2024-10-29/</link><description>路透周二的一项民意调查显示，中国10月份的工厂活动可能出现连续第六个月萎缩，但幅度很小，这支持了官员们的乐观态度，即近期的新刺激措施将使世界第二大经济体重回正轨。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 08:40:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-factory-activity-likely-contracted-oct-sixth-month-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，着眼于美国大选，中国考虑在未来几年额外举债超过1.4万亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/eyeing-us-election-china-considers-over-14-trillion-extra-debt-over-next-few-2024-10-29/</link><description>中国正在考虑下周批准在未来几年内发行超过10万亿元人民币（1.4万亿美元）的额外债务，以重振其脆弱的经济，如果唐纳德·特朗普赢得美国大选，这一财政计划预计将得到进一步支持。两个了解此事的消息来源。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 08:33:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/eyeing-us-election-china-considers-over-14-trillion-extra-debt-over-next-few-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜外长抵达俄罗斯远东地区 前往莫斯科</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/north-korean-foreign-minister-arrives-russian-far-east-heading-moscow-2024-10-29/</link><description>俄罗斯官方媒体称，朝鲜外交部长崔善姬周二抵达俄罗斯远东城市符拉迪沃斯托克，并将于周三访问莫斯科。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 08:04:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/north-korean-foreign-minister-arrives-russian-far-east-heading-moscow-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>热带风暴带来创纪录降雨，中国“夏威夷”被淹没</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-hawaii-under-water-tropical-storm-dumps-record-rainfall-2024-10-29/</link><description>在另一场热带气旋过境期间，被称为中国“夏威夷”的中国南部海南省连续第三天遭遇极端降雨，导致该岛半被淹没，遭遇了一年来创纪录的潮湿天气。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 08:03:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-hawaii-under-water-tropical-storm-dumps-record-rainfall-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>印尼普拉博沃首次出访将访问中国和美国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesias-prabowo-visit-china-us-first-foreign-trip-newspaper-says-2024-10-29/</link><description>据《罗盘报》周二报道，印度尼西亚总统普拉博沃·苏比安托将在上任几周后对中国和美国进行五国访问，这表明他有意在国际舞台上发挥积极作用。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 06:51:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesias-prabowo-visit-china-us-first-foreign-trip-newspaper-says-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>阿迪达斯报告称自 2022 年初以来中国销量最强劲</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/adidas-reports-rise-china-sales-third-quarter-2024-10-29/</link><description>阿迪达斯第三季度在大中华区实现强劲增长，而得益于品牌形象的改善，北美地区（不包括 Yeezy 鞋款）的销售额同比增长。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 06:50:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/adidas-reports-rise-china-sales-third-quarter-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>美国主要盟友日本的选举冲击可能会鼓舞中国和其他竞争对手</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/election-shock-key-us-ally-japan-could-embolden-china-other-rivals-2024-10-29/</link><description>华盛顿主要的亚洲安全盟友日本的选举结果令人震惊，而美国下周可能会破坏稳定的总统选举，可能会为中国和其他竞争对手提供一个考验西方在东亚的决心的机会。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 06:21:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/election-shock-key-us-ally-japan-could-embolden-china-other-rivals-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>TikTok母公司字节跳动创始人跃居中国富豪榜榜首</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/founder-tiktok-owner-bytedance-jumps-top-chinas-rich-list-2024-10-29/</link><description>周二公布的年度富豪榜显示，字节跳动创始人张一鸣是中国首富，个人财富为 493 亿美元，尽管房地产和可再生能源领域的同行表现不佳。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 05:36:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/founder-tiktok-owner-bytedance-jumps-top-chinas-rich-list-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>卢比与人民币疲软和当地股市下跌作斗争</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/rupee-battles-yuan-weakness-losses-local-equities-2024-10-29/</link><description>由于人民币贬值以及外资流出导致当地股市下跌，印度卢比周二仍面临压力。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 05:30:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/rupee-battles-yuan-weakness-losses-local-equities-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>什么是“台独”？台湾已经独立了吗？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/what-is-taiwan-independence-is-taiwan-already-independent-2024-10-29/</link><description>中国表示不会放弃使用武力将台湾置于其控制之下。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 05:03:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/what-is-taiwan-independence-is-taiwan-already-independent-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国习近平敦促拜登改变对台湾问题的措辞</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-xi-pressed-biden-alter-language-taiwan-sources-say-2024-10-29/</link><description>消息人士告诉路透社，中国希望美国说“我们反对台独”，而不是目前的版本，即美国“不支持”台独。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 05:02:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-xi-pressed-biden-alter-language-taiwan-sources-say-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>由于季度利润超出预期，汇丰银行对改造成本节约讳莫如深</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-third-quarter-profit-rises-10-beats-estimates-2024-10-29/</link><description>由于财富和批发银行收入的增长，汇丰控股周二超出了第三季度利润预期，但投资者仍在等待有关其结构彻底改革将如何节省成本的更多细节。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 04:14:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-third-quarter-profit-rises-10-beats-estimates-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国将利用神舟十九号将第十四次载人航天任务送入太空</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/china-send-14th-crewed-mission-space-shenzhou-19-2024-10-29/</link><description>中国将于周三将三名宇航员送入近地轨道，这是该国第14次载人航天任务，届时将进行数十项科学实验。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 03:13:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/china-send-14th-crewed-mission-space-shenzhou-19-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>面对美国国债收益率上升和资金外流，卢比将保持挑衅态度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/rupee-remain-defiant-face-higher-us-yields-outflows-2024-10-29/</link><description>印度卢比周二开盘可能几乎没有变化，在印度储备银行可能进行干预的情况下，对美国国债收益率、资本外流和其他外部信号反应迟钝。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 02:51:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/rupee-remain-defiant-face-higher-us-yields-outflows-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>美国高级外交官抵达台湾，官员淡化特朗普言论</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/senior-us-diplomat-arrives-taiwan-officials-downplay-trump-comments-2024-10-29/</link><description>美国事实上的大使馆周二表示，一名帮助管理与台湾关系的美国高级外交官已抵达台北，台湾官员试图淡化唐纳德·特朗普最近对台湾关键芯片产业和国防需求的攻击。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 02:48:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/senior-us-diplomat-arrives-taiwan-officials-downplay-trump-comments-2024-10-29/</guid></item></channel></rss>